r-iOS\/POIAlongRouteExample"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/AnimatedLineExample":{"title":"Animated Line","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnimatedLineExample","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/animatedlineexample","kind":"article","role":"article","abstract":[{"text":"Add an animated line to a map","type":"text"}]}}}